The '''portrayal of transgender people in the media''' list includes portrayals of [[transgender people]] and many other non-[[cisgender]] identities in the [[mass media]].
==Terminology== [[Transgender]] (trans) is the state of one's [[gender identity]] or gender expression not matching one's [[Sex assignment|assigned sex]]. Transgender men are people [[Sex assignment|assigned]] female at birth who identify as men. Transgender women are people [[Sex assignment|assigned]] male at birth who identify as women. Some gender nonconforming people do not [[Gender identity|identify]] with either male or female. [[Cisgender]] men and women are individuals whose gender experiences conform to the sex assigned to them at birth.
